见：§3.4 自定义物品模型



bowl的json文件
assets/minecraft/models/item/bowl.json{
    "parent": "item/generated",
    "textures": {
        "layer0": "item/bowl"
    },
        "overrides": [
                { "predicate": { "custom_model_data": 1001 }, "model": "minecraft:custom/boow"}
        ]
}复制代码

然后boow.json，assets/minecraft/models/custom/boow.json，内容如下{
    "parent": "item/generated",
    "textures": {
        "layer0": "custom/boooow"
    }
}复制代码


最后boooow.png的贴图文件，assets/minecraft/textures/custom/boooow.png





要问问题请把你不行的包发上来，至少清楚是哪里错了，只是要参考的话可以去隔壁板块找，省一个伸手
